=========================================

if we want to fetch list of cyurrently visible  items from RecyclerView 

then we need to call	
	layoutManager.getChildCount();// 6


if we want to fetch list of total items in adapter from RecyclerView

then we nedd to call
	 layoutManager.getItemCount();// 10



Scrolled out of the screen

	layoutManager.firstFindVisibleItemPosition(); // 2



VisibleItems = 6
TotalItems = 10
Scrolled Out Items = 2

Visible Items + ScrolledOut Items == Total Items  // if true then we have to fetch new data 
 

 
